[30;1m52 | [0m[35mCertain control plane and long-running operations for Cloud Storage (including Folder[0m
[30;1m53 | [0m[35mand Managed Folder operations) are supported via the `Storage Control Client`_.[0m

[30;1m477 | [0m[35m        if self.end is not None and end_byte >= self.end:[0m
